name: CNN
text: The Trump administration has reached a $1.525 billion deal with Moderna Inc. to manufacture and deliver 100 million doses of the company’s Covid-19 vaccine once it is approved, according to a news release from the US Department of Health and Human Services https://t.co/eGSgVMiW9S

name: CNN
text:
The North Georgia State Fair has been canceled for the first time since World War II. It was scheduled to begin next month.

Organizers are planning to hold a “Taste of the Fair” drive-thru experience, giving people a chance to taste favorite fair foods. https://t.co/8vOQcpedqh
